# Azure Deployment Summary — ReadingTimeDemo

## Deployment Files

| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `infra/main.bicep` | Main Bicep template orchestrating all 9 Azure resource modules |
| `infra/main.parameters.json` | Deployment parameters (environment, location, container name) |
| `infra/modules/identity.bicep` | User-Assigned Managed Identity for all service-to-service auth |
| `infra/modules/registry.bicep` | Azure Container Registry with AcrPull role for MI |
| `infra/modules/loganalytics.bicep` | Log Analytics Workspace for Container Apps telemetry |
| `infra/modules/appinsights.bicep` | Application Insights connected to Log Analytics |
| `infra/modules/keyvault.bicep` | Key Vault storing App Insights connection string (RBAC auth) |
| `infra/modules/appconfig.bicep` | Azure App Configuration with Data Reader role for MI |
| `infra/modules/storage.bicep` | Storage Account with `static-assets` blob container (local auth disabled) |
| `infra/modules/containerappenv.bicep` | Container Apps Environment connected to Log Analytics |
| `infra/modules/containerapp.bicep` | Container App (User-assigned MI, CORS, .NET 10, port 8080) |
| `infra/deploy.sh` | Full provision + build + deploy script (Linux/macOS) |
| `infra/deploy.ps1` | Full provision + build + deploy script (Windows PowerShell) |
| `infra/README.md` | Infrastructure documentation and usage guide |
| `infra/compliance.md` | IaC rules compliance report (24/24 rules applied) |
| `infra/infra-config.md` | Machine-readable Azure resource summary (template, update post-provision) |
| `src/ReadingTimeDemo/Dockerfile` | Updated: .NET 10, non-root user (UID 1001), HEALTHCHECK, port 8080 |
| `src/ReadingTimeDemo/.dockerignore` | Build context exclusions (bin, obj, git, secrets) |
| `.github/modernize/modernization-plan/004-deployment-azure-container-apps/plan.md` | Deployment plan with architecture, steps, and tracking |
| `.github/modernize/modernization-plan/004-deployment-azure-container-apps/progress.md` | Real-time deployment progress log |
| `.github/modernize/modernization-plan/004-deployment-azure-container-apps/deployment-summary.md` | Deployment summary and quick reference |
| `.github/modernize/modernization-plan/004-deployment-azure-container-apps/deploy-scripts/deploy-app.sh` | Standalone app image build + Container App update script |

