## Deployment Status

> ⚠️ **Infrastructure provisioning blocked** — `brntbeer@githubazure.com` requires **Contributor** role on subscription `5b97b8de-e4f7-4787-a860-bcdc1130e599` to create resource groups and provision resources.

### To complete deployment once permissions are granted:

```bash
# Full provision + build + deploy (Linux/macOS)
chmod +x infra/deploy.sh
./infra/deploy.sh rg-readingtimedemo eastus prod
```

```powershell
# Full provision + build + deploy (Windows)
.\infra\deploy.ps1 -ResourceGroup rg-readingtimedemo -Location eastus -EnvironmentName prod
```
